    <div class="article-titles__inner print-hidden"><p class="article-type"><a href="/series/the-breakdown" class="article-type__link article-type__link--type">The Breakdown</a></p><h1 class="article-title">Who Is Collecting Data from Your&nbsp;Car?</h1>
      <p class="article-subhead">
        
          A firehose of sensitive data from your vehicle is flowing to a group of companies you’ve probably never heard of 
        
        
          
<span class="article-author">
  <span>By </span>
  

    

      <a class="article-author__link" href="https://themarkup.org/people/jon-keegan/">Jon Keegan</a> and 

      <a class="article-author__link" href="https://themarkup.org/people/alfred-ng/">Alfred Ng</a> 
</span>

        
      </p>
      <div class="article-date">
        <time datetime="2022-07-27T08:00:00">July 27, 2022 08:00 ET</time></div>

      
        <figcaption class='article-caption'>
          <span class='article-caption-label'></span>
          
